values: Alright, well I am changing my livejournal name to Black_ribbon. So add my new name. K guys?
Hey guys guess what?  I GOT MY LICENSE!!! Woot!

How can liking one person so much effect how you are to other people in your life? How can they have so much control over somebody else's life and not even notice it? How can being infatuated with someone take you over, how can it be that sooner or later it becomes all that is important in your life? Like nothing or nobody else matters? It is a horrible pain in your stomach, like somone is just kicking you over and over again. Your friends soon become so sick of the bickering and constant talk of it that they just leave you there to feel how you always dreaded feeling, alone. It's like they could save you from death but they no longer care that they lead you there instead of saving you. Don't ever let anyone think you are aren't the greatest person in the world when you know you are. 

Joel thank you for being there for me today when I needed you. You truly are a wonderful person. 

- Tina.

So yeah, today went to go see my brother. I get my license in 3 days, asuming I pass. That will be some good shit, I'm tired of always depending on other people for rides. Going cosmic bowling tonight!! woo hoo. You know, life is going good for once. Happy day after valentines day! Love you guys, tina

Today I went driving with Angela and Carrie, and when I was pulling up to the driveway I accidently went over a pothole and I swerved to fix my mistake and swerved into the other lane. Luckily there were no cars and Angela didn't freak. Well, 6 more days till I go for my test. woot! Steph I love you and I'm sorry I wasn't home. Remember to tell me what you want for lunch on wednesday. I'm bringing it to you!!!! Oh, yeah I got you something.

Well today I went to the high school. then I came to Samamntha's. I had hellof fun. We were calling hell of people. I go take my driver's test on February 18. I am so scared. Wish me luck everybody!!!well i got to go, talk to you later guys!. -tina

I'm not happy. My life isn't going to good lately. It isn't going good at all. I hate it. I want to move. I want to move as far away as possible. I think the only person that keeps me somewhat sane is Bo. He keeps me up and going. He is what makes me happy. Don't get me wrong I love all my friends. But it's different with Bo. I went to Modesto, apparently I'm an intimidating floozy who can't be trusted. That's what my friend's mom told her. It's because Cheri is with my ex, the one I thought I was in love with, and they are going to get married. It's funny that her mother call me that, because Cheri was sleeping with Mario when me and him were together. I guess I just wasn't good enough. He isn't happy with her, I know it. He completeley changes, I don't think he is ready to settle. He is only 20. Why would he settle so early. I think he is just afraid to leave. But, I don't know. -Tina

The other night Me and my Mom got into this really horrible fight. She really hurt my feelings. Anyway, she said this really horible thing to me. It hurt so bad that she didn't realize it. But I was really mad, and I was up from 4 in the morning to about 7:30 taking down all my pictures and posters and other stuff I had tacked to my walls. It took for ever. I took down almost 200 pictures, 6 posters and a whole bunch of other shit. But now my room is totally bare and all I have left are 2 shelves. But I am going to repaint my room, so yeah.
I went to school today to go to art lab. It was closed which fucking sucked, I have to get that shit over with. Anyway I was standing outside waiting for my ride and I saw Greg, I hadn't seen him in so long. That really made my day. He looks really good. I hell of miss him.

What would you do if for every moment you were truly happy there would be 10 moments of sadness?
What would you do if your best friend died tomorrow and you never got to tell them how you felt?
What would you do if you loved someone more than anything else and you could never have them?
What would you do if everytime you loved someone you had to say goodbye?
What would you do if everytime you wanted someone they would never be there? 

- Tina Vasquez

Hey guys my new phone # is 925 354 6460. call me please. tina.

Im talking to Alex, he called and my phone was hell of loud and it woke up Carrie. Oops. I'm chatting with Joel, we have been chatting for about 3 hours or something around that. I don't know. Carrie is asleep now. My butt really hurts from sitting on this chair for so long. Man I miss BO. I think he is mad at me, he has'nt returned any of my phone calls at all. I think he is avoiding me. Do you think? I hope not. If I did anything, Im Sorry. I always seem to do something wrong, sometimes I think I should just stop talking, this way I can't make a fool out of myself, you know? I can never think of the right things to say. Why is that? I miss going to Antioch. I feel so out of place when I go hang out there now. Like people are staring at me and talking behind my back. I think I am just a very paranoid person. I always make the worst of things. I'm sorry I ruin our good times.

Today my friend Krystiana came over, we went to Carls JR. When we were walking back and we pulled up to the cross walk I heard somebody shout my name. I couldnt figure it out until I saw a body hanging outside of a passenger side window. It was... Brian Warner. It was really funny. I guess you had to be there. When he started to pass us he screamed "Bye Tina. Rock on!" 
    Then we went back to my place and watched Zoolander. She went home after a while. Carrie and her mom came to pick me up. I am staying over here for the night.                                                           I miss BO. I miss him a lot. I havent talked to him in a while. I talked to him the other night, I was having a bad day. He said something that made me really upset, he made me cry. I was crying a lot. Steph made me feel better though. Me and her are'nt as close as we used to be though. I just don't think I'm as fun or exciting as her other friends. I met the almighty Alena. She was cool. And really beautiful as well.
It's funny how one little thing can change someones whole perspective on another person. Jimmy, I miss you.

I just got back from being in modesto for over a week. I came home early so i could see nick. We were supposed to hang out yesterday but when I called he wasnt home turns out he was hanging with Steph and Alvin. Today is his last full day here, this bites I really wanted to hang out with him or at least get to see him for a few minutes. I guess that's not happening. There is always next time. I guess him and a few people are going to go to S.F. today. He did invite me, but I'm not really comftorable around other people. It's an insecurity thing. I don't feel like I fit in very well.But that's my own fault. Well, Nick, I miss you, see you next time. - Tina.

does time really cure pain? if it does how long does it take? nothing can cure pain, it lasts forever, its never completly cured its just tucked away, in the back of your heart and mind with heavy books and boxes stacked on top.

I just got back from job hunting, I don't think I did very well, eh, oh well. Me and Stephanie went, but she didn't job hunt, she just accompanied me. I went to the winter ball on Saturday, ,I forgot how many hot guys went to Antioch. woo wee, hmm, but i dont really have anything to say, so buh bye.

hey all, whats up? today i had to go give melissa the money for the winter ball. i hope i have fun its in 2 days, i have this gut feeling something terrible is going to happen, not too terrible but enough to ruin my night. hmm,... my mom finished my dress last night it looks really good. i like it a lot. now i have to figure out how i am going to do my hair, its so short that i really cant do anything with  it, which really bites, but i guess ill figure something out. i worked the last 2 nights graveyard, im waiting for the boss to pay me. well wish me luck, talk to yal later, tina...   ps, im really tired, so if you saw me today pardon my tiredness
why is it that one person can come between such good friends?

If someone is beautiful on the outside, do people really believe that it makes them beautiful on the inside? What exactly is this world coming to when everyone is judged on what they wear and how they look?

Well today I went to the high school. I am supposed to go to Brian's house with Stephanie after she gets out. I saw Codi today, its been a while since I've talked to him. But I have homework to finish tonight. I have school tomorrow, which bites cause I also have one more computer our to do for Bio. But Steph invited me to the winter ball which is cool cause my mom said I can go. I'm making her make my dress. It's really pretty. Bo and his gal are going, it will be the first time I've seen them since together since they have started going out, it's gonna hurt but I will tyr my best to let it not show. Wish me luck :)
